Presentation, survival prospects, and predictors of death in Eisenmenger 
syndrome: a combined retrospective and case-control study.

Diller GP(1), Dimopoulos K, Broberg CS, Kaya MG, Naghotra US, Uebing A, Harries 
C, Goktekin O, Gibbs JS, Gatzoulis MA.

Author information:
(1)Adult Congenital Heart Centre and Centre for Pulmonary Hypertension, Royal 
